...Ah! That's right! I was entrusted with the
battery from the doctor!

Esuka! Please, somehow pull yourself together
with this...!

Thank goodness we brought anti-tank weapons based
on the information from before!
Ugh... I let my guard down...

Esuka was riddled with bullets from the anti-tank
machine gun...
エスカは対戦車機関銃でハチの巣にされてしまった…
任務に失敗してしまった…！

Esuka was blasted with a high-powered laser and
ended up being torn to pieces...
任務に失敗してしまった…！

Esuka was blasted with a high-powered laser and
ended up being torn to pieces...

Esuka was caught by the climax machine, and in
front of the enemy, she climaxed over and over
again until her neural circuits were burnt out.

I was captured by the imperial soldiers... Some
time passed after that...
Damn it! Let go! Esuka! Where is Esuka...!

What, you came to save that piece of junk...
You're quite underestimated, coming all alone!

Hehehe... If you want to see her that badly, I'll
arrange it for you.

When I heard you were captured, I went on a
rampage until I was like this. It was tough!
Hahaha!
